The `sorry` in the original proof was in the line where we tried to compose the smoothness of the coordinate change with the smoothness of `f` and `g`. The issue was that we needed to show that `n ≤ ⊤`, which is trivially true because `⊤` is the highest element in `ℕ∞`. 

